text: Richard Tamble (born July 26, 1945) is an American wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 52 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:American male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United States Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Inglewood, California
